<p class="blockintro">Course documents are any printed material that you might handout that is not part of an assignment.</p>
<div class="block">
<p><label for="document_title" class="required">Title:</label>
<%= text_field 'document', 'title'  %></p>

<p><label for="file">File:</label>
<%= file_field_tag "file" %></p>

<p><label for="document_comments">Comments:</label>
<%= text_area 'document', 'comments'  %></p>
</div>

<p class="blockintro">Publication control. <em>Visible after</em> allows you to schedule documents for future publication, as long as the <em>Visible</em> setting is set to <strong>Yes</strong>.</p>
<div class="block">
<p><label for="document_created_at" class="required">Visible after:</label>
<%= datetime_select 'document', 'created_at'  %></p>

<p><label for="document_published" class="required">Visible:</label>
	<%= radio_button 'document', 'published', true %> Yes
	<%= radio_button 'document', 'published', false %> No</p>
</div>
